:: Enable Anonymous on Default Web Site\CFIDE\ncscript %windir%\system32\inetsrv\adsutil.vbs set w3svc/1/root/CFIDE/AccessFlags 5\n\n:: Disable Anonymous and Enable NTLM for the Default Web Site (except CFIDE)\ncscript %windir%\system32\inetsrv\adsutil.vbs set w3svc/1/root/AuthNTLM 1\ncscript %windir%\system32\inetsrv\adsutil.vbs set w3svc/1/root/AuthAnonymous 0\n\n:: Example of setting NTLM for another directory, e.g., WebApp1\ncscript %windir%\system32\inetsrv\adsutil.vbs set w3svc/1/root/WebApp1/AuthNTLM 1\ncscript %windir%\system32\inetsrv\adsutil.vbs set w3svc/1/root/WebApp1/AuthAnonymous 0